    libdft-dr v0.1: DynamoRIO-native re-implementation of the
    libdft64 data-flow model, including the public libdft_dr::
    API surface (lifecycle, tag model, sources, sinks), the
    interned-label tag-map representation, the sink registries
    (opcode-class, PC-range, function-entry), and the four
    reference clients.

